title.rendered: HSP TailAssist Single Action Tail Gate Strut – Mazda BT50 Gen 2 2011- 2020 (Series Up & Ur)

content.rendered:
HSP TailAssist Single Action Tail Gate Strut – Mazda BT50 Gen 2 2011- 2020 (Series Up & Ur) (Dampening only)

The Tail Gate Assist is a fantastic addition to a vehicles tailgate. Using a one-way strut system that dampens the weight while the tailgate is declining and the factory torsion bar reduces the weight when inclining. Utilising factory mounting points makes the installation a breeze as there is no need to remove the tailgate.

– Dampens weight of the tailgate when declining.
– The factory torsion bar reduces weight when inclining.
– One strut system.
– Non-Intrusive design.
